resources NI(12)
notes
This experiment aims to investigate acceleration mechanism of the lower 
thermospheric neutral wind by magnetospheric energy input (i.e. Joule heating 
and ion drag effects). CP2 mode will be used for the ESR observation to obtain 
data of the neutral wind velocity vector in the lower thermosphere. We prefer 
geomagnetic disturbed conditions.

